Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition
On February 3, 2005, AutoNation, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing its results of operations for the fiscal quarter ended December 31, 2004. A copy of the press release and related quarterly financial data supplement is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report and is incorporated herein by reference.
