     AutoNation, Inc., headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., is America's largest automotive retailer. Ranked No. 97 on the 2004 Fortune 500 and a component of the Standard and Poor's 500 Index, AutoNation employs approximately 28,000 people and owns and operates 358 new vehicle franchises in 17 states. For additional information, please visit , where more than 100,000 vehicles are available for sale.
