Item 8.01 Other Events.
On March 7, 2006, AutoNation, Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing that it intends to commence an offer to purchase for cash any and all of its outstanding 9% senior notes due 2008 in an aggregate principal amount of $323.5 million (the "Offer"). The Company expects to commence the Offer by no later than March 10, 2006. A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and its contents are incorporated herein by reference. On March 7, 2006, the Company also issued a press release announcing that it intends to offer up to $900 million aggregate principal amount of senior unsecured notes. A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.2 hereto and its contents are incorporated herein by reference.
