Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits.
Exhibit No. Description 99.1 Press Release, dated April 5, 2006, issued by AutoNation, Inc. announcing the pricing for its cash tender offer and consent solicitation in respect of its outstanding 9% Senior Notes due 2008. 99.2 Press Release, dated April 5, 2006, issued by AutoNation, Inc. announcing the pricing of $600.0 million aggregate principal amount of senior unsecured fixed rate notes and senior unsecured floating rate notes.
