Exhibit B
          (D) if such Restricted Definitive Note is being transferred pursuant to an exemption from the registration requirements of the Securities Act in accordance with Rule 144 under the Securities Act, a certificate to the effect set forth in hereto, including the certifications in item (3)(a) thereof;
Exhibit B
          (E) if such Restricted Definitive Note is being transferred to an Institutional Accredited Investor in reliance on an exemption from the registration requirements of the Securities Act other than those listed in subparagraphs (B) through (D) above, a certificate to the effect set forth in hereto, including the certifications, certificates and Opinion of Counsel required by item (3)(d) thereof, if applicable;
Exhibit B
