"Good Reason" shall mean the occurrence of any of the following: (i) a material change by the Company in the Executive's duties or responsibilities which would cause Executive's position with the Company to become of materially and substantially less responsibility and importance than those associated with his duties or responsibilities as of the date hereof; or (ii) a material breach of this Agreement by the Company, which breach is not cured within ten (10) days after written notice thereof is received by the Company.
(c) Upon termination of the Employment Period hereunder, at the Company's request the Executive shall resign from the Company's Board of Directors.
