(c) that, notwithstanding anything to the contrary in the Credit Agreement, Term Loans made or outstanding on the Effective Date may be converted to Eurodollar Loans on two (2) Business Days' notice to the Administrative Agent delivered on or before 2:00 p.m. on the Effective Date.
