Exempt Group
2. The Company hereby represents and warrants that: (i) as of July 19, 2010, there were 146,389,924 shares of Common Stock issued and outstanding and (ii) on March 31, 2010, there were 169,853,517 shares of Common Stock issued and outstanding.
 
