AutoNation, Inc., headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., is America's largest automotive retailer and has been named America's Most Admired Automotive Retailer by FORTUNE Magazine five times. A component of the Standard and Poor's 500 Index, AutoNation owned and operated 243 new vehicle franchises in 15 states as of March 31, 2011. For additional information, please visit or .
