2.16 . The proceeds of the Loans and the Letters of Credit issued pursuant to the Letter of Credit Facility shall be used by the Borrower and its Subsidiaries to repay indebtedness, finance acquisitions and for working capital, capital expenditures, share repurchases and other general corporate purposes of the Borrower and its Subsidiaries.
