first
quarter conference call may be accessed by telephone at (888) 769-8515 (password: AutoNation) at 11:00 a.m. Eastern Time or on AutoNations investor relations website at
investors.autonation.com
.
The webcast will also be available on our website under Events & Presentations following the call. A playback of the conference call will be available after 1:00 p.m. Eastern Time on
April 25, 2012
, through May 2, 2012 by calling (888) 568-0151 (password: 75300).
 
 
